                    <div class="art-tit cont-tit">
                        <h3>关于西安市长安区医院病理科相关耗材项目的院内磋商公告</h3>
                        <p>
                            <span><img src="../../images/art-zz.png" alt="">作者：</span>
                            <span><img src="../../images/art-sj.png" alt="">发布时间：2026-07-10</span>
                            <span><img src="../../images/art-djs.png" alt="">浏览次数：<script>_showDynClicks("wbnews", 2121014573, 8258)</script></span>
                        </p>
